				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Cinc.</placeName> <date>July 14<hi rend="sup">th</hi> 5614</date>. A M.</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Rev. Sir&#33;</p>
			<p rend="indent(4)">According to my Promise&#44; I send<lb/> You the newborn Israelite&#59; it was <hi rend="underline">born</hi><lb/> &#38; <hi rend="underline">delivered</hi> to its <hi rend="underline">94</hi> Aborments on the <add>Hebrew</add><lb/> &#40;<add>Hebrew</add>&#41; &#38; sold <hi rend="underline">on the streets</hi> by the Newspapers Boys<lb/> among others&#44; on the same Day &#38; <date>Sunday</date> enst&#8212;among<lb/> the <sic>Gentils</sic> to preat<add>&#63;</add> abroad <add>Hebrew</add>&#59;&#8212;Sir&#44; You will be<lb/> amazed by reading a Jewish history in it&#8212;<lb/> &#40;&#58;Le premier Chef&#45;D&#39;oeuvre&#58;&#41; containing a <sic>discription</sic><lb/> which can only be expected of an <hi rend="underline"><persName>Eisenmenger</persName></hi><lb/> united with the entirely <hi rend="underline">Ignorance</hi> of our<lb/> Rabbinical Laws &#38; Cassuites&#44; &#40;over a <add>Hebrew</add> &#40;as he discribes<add>&#63;</add>&#58;&#41;<lb/> needs not to be send <add>Hebrew</add>&#8212;nor has a brother or<lb/> sister to mourn <add>Hebrew</add>&#8212;neither is necessary to keep<lb/> you &#38; to say <add>Hebrew</add> or learn a <add>Hebrew</add> as he means it.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)">The whole shows <del><add>&#63;</add></del> evidently his Attention<lb/> to abuse our rabbinical Laws &#38; to make our<lb/> holy Religion ridiculous in the sight of the <sic>Gentils</sic><lb/> <hi rend="underline">using</hi> every <hi rend="underline">means</hi>&#44; even <add>Hebrew</add> &#38; absurdity&#33;&#8212;<lb/> this is his only Happy&#8212;he is a <add>Hebrew</add> in<lb/> the real sense of the word&#8212;next more&#8212;</p>
			<p rend="indent(7)">I remain&#44; Dr. Sir&#44;</p>
			<p rend="indent(8)">Your most obdt &#38; respect<add>&#63;</add></p>
			<p rend="indent(9)"><persName role="author">Dr. J. Mayer</persName></p>
